{"tid":54143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"既然港人大將可能要放棄外國籍及效忠，港公務員是否應跟隨？","createTime":"2016-12-25T09:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T10:40:11.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99aed1b31d01807486d875ab31b5ad237a90af97","tid":54143,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:55:11.000Z","msg":"9月立法會選舉，選舉事務處加入效忠《基本法》確認書，並以此作為取消參選人資格的理由，引起社會廣泛迴響；有份出席北京全國人大常委會會議的港區人大代表馬逢國透露，明年換屆的港區全國人大代表選舉亦將修訂選舉規則，在報名登記表上須聲明效忠中華人民共和國及香港特別行政區，以及擁護憲法和《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\n馬逢國認為有關改動與香港近來出現港獨、分離和自決等主張有關，但認為變動對參選人合理，影響不大。另一名人大代表田北辰則指，新增規定等於要參選人放棄外國護照，因為人大代表等同國會議員，有份選國家主席，絕不能雙重效忠。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161225/56090820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161225%2F56090820&d=AQLeV2imW%2F1VcvO7yNlXRGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=dd09a643\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161225%2F56090820&h=7edc3d73\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161225/56090820</a>"},{"pid":"b04d4d7b8ee9a0e01da27df533e8f6e9f4ccde7f","tid":54143,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba97a0ebcad914fa1e3a7e2d2314282a8c70100","tid":54143,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}